== Bug Fixes ==
* Fixed bug with cached file error occasionally displaying

= Release 1.0.7 =
== Features ==
* download_file_with_fread($remote_url='', $local_filename='')
* download_file_with_curl($remote_url='', $local_filename='', $use_cookies=false, $cookie_jar_filename='')
* cache_remote_file($options=array())
== Bug Fixes ==
* Converted "download_file" function to be a pointer for "download_file_with_fread"

